<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/14801ALJMRBKMVHTKGLRNMTGKCGDBTVSP> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "Cuban Vibes: A Symphonic Festival ";
  schema:description """
	CONDUCTOR: Cosette Justo Valdés<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>GUEST ARTISTS:<span><br/></span>Milagros de Los Angeles Soto, soprano<span><br/></span>Mayquel González, trumpet<span><br/></span>Harold López-Nussa, piano<span><br/></span>Ruy López-Nussa, drums<span><br/></span>Yandy Martínez González, double bass<span><br/></span>Roberto Vizcaino Jr., Cuban percussion<span><br/></span>Miguel Valdés, trumpet, Cuban percussion<span><br/></span>Phil Dwyer, saxophones<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>A thrilling evening filled with the rhythm, passion and joy of Cuban music! Join Artistic Director Cosette Justo Valdés and her amazing guests for an evening of virtuosity and fun! Romantic arias from Cuban operettas, Cuban jazz standards and more will make this evening the perfect way to spend Valentine’s Day!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>
""";
