<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/54001ABPSKBMMLLGTRJBVNRVDRDQRLGJK> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "DANCESTREAMS: Dance Odyssey 2026";
  schema:description """
	Celebrating the 25th anniversary of Dance Odyssey, for one show only, studios from across Vancouver Island and the surrounding Gulf Islands bring youth together on stage at Nanaimo's Port Theatre. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This non-competitive celebration of dance on the Island features diverse styles such as ballet, contemporary, jazz, lyrical, tap, hip hop and more! <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Dancestreams/VIYDTA hosts the event and will premiere two new commissions choreographed by guest artists Sarah Hutton and Sophie Dow and performed by Dancestreams 25/26 dance artists. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Photo credit: 24/25 Dancestreams artists in 'Drift'. Photo by: Aidan R <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>
""";
