<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/48601ARPGPBJPBBJPGRVPTHVCMTBCKDRT> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "Nanaimo Comedy Classic";
  schema:description """
	Need a laugh?  After selling out theatres from coast-to-coast, Jokers Canada is thrilled to finally be making its Nanaimo debut in March with an all-star lineup of our country’s BEST pro comedians. Save money by purchasing online in advance. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Scheduled Performers: <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Damonde Tschritter: (HBO / Conan + Winner Of International Comedy Festival In Seattle)  <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://youtu.be/u44ZiVvFgMc?si=iVzpR-JiVVE4941j\"> YouTube</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Ryan Williams: (Just For Laughs + CBC Debaters) <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://youtu.be/o_8o9zFTEkg?si=CogspCE25HBcQ_Tm\"> YouTube</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Syd Bosel: (Canada’s Got Talent + Winnipeg Comedy Festival)<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://youtu.be/T262h0YyD2U?si=EKg00iwrgNccWoTB\"> YouTube</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Adam Christie: (Winner Of Sirius XM Top Comic + Former lead writer for This Hour Has 22 Minutes) <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://youtu.be/hRKP6KHGmOU?si=6ZdlrsF94-QAoqvi\"> YouTube</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Aaron Arya: (National Touring + Departure Festival Toronto)<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://vimeo.com/649361798?fl=pl&amp;fe=vl\"> Vimeo</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>*lineup subject to change due to unforeseen circumstance <span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://jokerscanada.ca/home\"> jokerscanada.ca</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Follow @jokerscanada for more information.  <span><br/></span>Questions: info@jokerscanada.ca <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>*no refunds<span><br/></span>* this event is for an adult audience<span><br/></span> 
""";
