<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/42001AQJJQTSKLLKMRKNHHDRNVHRLPNPB> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "STICKY FINGERS - Tickets Available at Door";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">Tickets Available at Door</span><span><br/></span>Canada's tribute to The Rolling Stones @ The Queens<span class=\"BoldText\"><span><br/></span><span><br/></span></span><span class=\"BoldText\">START ME UP NANAIMO!!</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>\"When I closed my eyes I couldn't believe it wasn't Mick. All my faves. Top notch rock and roll musicians, all\" <span><br/></span>Vicki J. Campbell River<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>As featured on \"CBC On The Coast\", STICKY FINGERS is Canada's tribute to The Rolling Stones. Fronted by dynamic Londoner Stuart Turnbull as \"Mick\", STICKY FINGERS recreates the unmistakable energy, sound and swagger of the greatest Rock 'n' Roll band of all time. Showcasing hits spanning all 60 years of the Stones catalogue, every show is a full-throttle celebration of the music that defined a generation.  Sit back and enjoy - or dance your tail off to <span class=\"ItalicText\">Start Me Up  |  Sympathy for the Devil  | </span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Angry |  Satisfaction (I Can't Get No)  |  It's only Rock and Roll  |  Brown Sugar  |  Under </span><span class=\"ItalicText\">My Thumb  |  Wild Horses  |  You Can't Always Get What You Want  |  Paint it Black  | </span><span class=\"ItalicText\"> Can't You Hear Me Knocking  | Midnight Rambler | Gimme Shelter |  Jumping Jack </span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Flash</span> and many more...  <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>STICKY FINGERS is more than a tribute it's a Rolling Stones experience!  <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Recent reviews:<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Their performance was electrifying. <span><br/></span>\"Attended the show this evening. WOW the energy the group created with their performance weas electrifying. Thanks to those at The ACT who make the shows available for our community\". <span><br/></span>Shebe Parker, Maple Ridge BC<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Outstanding!<span><br/></span>\"Musically, very, very similar to the Stones (in fact if you closed your eyes you would swear that it was not Sticky Fingers but the actual Stones)\" <span><br/></span>Paul T. Entertainment Director - Legion 140  <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>A truly enjoyable Rolling Stones Tribute<span><br/></span>\"Just got back from the show, awesome time! Sticky Fingers puts on a truly enjoyable Rolling Stones Tribute. If they are coming anywhere close to where you are at make a point to go see them.... Sympathy for the Devil was lights out, as was the whole set.  Great Band.\"<span><br/></span>Greg E. Campbell River BC  <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>\"So much heart and soul put into the show. High energy. Stones fans will love it\".<span><br/></span>Kathy Cooper  <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Sticky Fingers Rocked The Park! <span><br/></span>\"Stuart was the perfect \"Mick\" both visually and vocally and the rest of the band was also spot on.  For anyone looking for a true Rolling Stones tribute experience, book this band. You won't be disappointed\". <span><br/></span>Lloyd D.  Entertainment Dir, Parksville Beachfest  <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Five Stars and more for this incredible band <span><br/></span>\"The dance floor was lively all night. Thank you so much for providing the Ultimate Rolling Stones Experience   <span><br/></span>Sylvia D. Booking Agent<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-02-20T19:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
