<http://www.spektrix.com/theporttheatre/event/61201ARKNPQJBTCNRNPMQMMBCRPGCCDLM> a
    schema:Event;
  schema:name "The 88th Key";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">Join the Heist for the premiere screening event of The 88th Key.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Your favourite Heisters are back! This time: on the big screen, with a film inspired by their original show: Keys are the Champions. Nico and Patrick join forces with a computer whiz/hacker and their mysterious agent to attempt to liberate the mythical last key of the piano. Featuring an original film score by Nico Rhodes, cinematography and screenplay by Patrick Schörle of Fractal FX Productions. See how many places you recognize in Nanaimo...<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Join us for an absolute blast of an event! Come as you are or dress up in attire that you would wear for a heist!  Meet & Greet with Piano Heist after the show and don’t forget to grab some wicked selfies on the red carpet and of course there will be cake!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>3 – 4:15 p.m.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The Big Screen Premiere – The 88th Key!<span><br/></span>Talk Back with Piano Heist – Nico & Patrick and Patrick Schörle, Host<span><br/></span>A Mini Performance by Piano Heist<span><br/></span>Meet & Greet in the lobby with cake
""";
